    category: 'Pasta',
    area: 'Italian',
    instructions: { en: 'Heat the oil in a large saucepan. Use kitchen scissors to snip the bacon into small pieces, or use a sharp knife to chop it on a chopping board. Add the bacon to the pan and cook for just a few mins until starting to turn golden. Add the onion, celery and carrot, and cook over a medium heat for 5 mins, stirring occasionally, until softened.\nAdd the garlic and cook for 1 min, then tip in the mince and cook, stirring and breaking it up with a wooden spoon, for about 6 mins until browned all over.\nStir in the tomato purée and cook for 1 min, mixing in well with the beef and vegetables. Tip in the chopped tomatoes. Fill each can half full with water to rinse out any tomatoes left in the can, and add to the pan. Add the honey and season to taste. Simmer for 20 mins.\nHeat oven to 200C/180C fan/gas 6. To assemble the lasagne, ladle a little of the ragu sauce into the bottom of the roasting tin or casserole dish, spreading the sauce all over the base. Place 2 sheets of lasagne on top of the sauce overlapping to make it fit, then repeat with more sauce and another layer of pasta. Repeat with a further 2 layers of sauce and pasta, finishing with a layer of pasta.\nPut the crème fraîche in a bowl and mix with 2 tbsp water to loosen it and make a smooth pourable sauce. Pour this over the top of the pasta, then top with the mozzarella. Sprinkle Parmesan over the top and bake for 25-30 mins until golden and bubbling. Serve scattered with basil, if you like.', ro: 'Incalziti uleiul intr-o cratita mare. Adaugati ceapa, telina si morcovul si gatiti 10 min. Adaugati usturoiul si gatiti 1 min. Adaugati carnea tocata si rumeniti. Adaugati rosiile, pasta de rosii, oregano si supa. Aduceti la fierbere si gatiti pe foc mic 30 min.\n\nPentru sosul alb, topiti untul, adaugati faina si gatiti 1 min. Adaugati laptele treptat, amestecand continuu. Gatiti pana se ingroasa. Adaugati nucsoara si condimentati.\n\nPreincalziti cuptorul la 200C. Intr-o tava, alternati straturi de sos de carne, foi de lasagna si sos alb. Terminati cu sos alb si presarati parmesan. Coapteti 30-35 min pana este auriu si fierbe.', ru: 'Разогрейте масло в большой кастрюле. Добавьте лук, сельдерей и морковь и готовьте 10 мин. Добавьте чеснок и готовьте 1 мин. Добавьте фарш и обжарьте. Добавьте помидоры, томатную пасту, орегано и бульон. Доведите до кипения и варите на слабом огне 30 мин.\n\nДля белого соуса растопите масло, добавьте муку и готовьте 1 мин. Постепенно влейте молоко, непрерывно помешивая. Готовьте до загустения. Добавьте мускатный орех и приправьте.\n\nРазогрейте духовку до 200C. В форме чередуйте слои мясного соуса, листов лазаньи и белого соуса. Закончите белым соусом и посыпьте пармезаном. Запекайте 30-35 мин до золотистости и кипения.', es: 'Caliente el aceite en una cacerola grande. Agregue la cebolla, el apio y la zanahoria y cocine 10 min. Agregue el ajo y cocine 1 min. Agregue la carne molida y dore. Agregue los tomates, el pure de tomate, el oregano y el caldo. Lleve a ebullicion y cocine a fuego bajo 30 min.\n\nPara la salsa blanca, derrita la mantequilla, agregue la harina y cocine 1 min. Agregue la leche gradualmente, revolviendo continuamente. Cocine hasta que espese. Agregue nuez moscada y sazone.\n\nPrecaliente el horno a 200C. En un molde, alterne capas de salsa de carne, laminas de lasana y salsa blanca. Termine con salsa blanca y espolvoree parmesano. Hornee 30-35 min hasta que este dorado y burbujeante.' },
