    id: '53105',
    name: { en: 'Spiced smoky barbecued chicken', ro: 'Pui la gratar afumat condimentat', ru: 'Копчёная курица барбекю со специями', es: 'Pollo ahumado a la barbacoa con especias' },
    category: 'Chicken',
    area: 'Australian',
    instructions: { en: 'Make the marinade. Smash the garlic with a little salt using a pestle and mortar. Add the lemon zest and juice, the spice mix, chilli, oil and a good grinding of black pepper. Mix to a paste. This can be done in a mini food processor.\n\nToss the chicken in the marinade and set aside while you light the barbecue. When the barbecue\'s hot, lay the bunches of herbs on the grid and put the chicken, skin side up, on top. Close the lid, if your barbecue has one, and cook the chicken on the smouldering herbs for about 10 minutes until the meat starts to colour. Turn the chicken and continue to cook for a further 20-30 minutes, turning as necessary, until it is slightly charred from the burnt herbs and cooked through to the bone.', ro: 'Zdrobiti usturoiul cu sare. Amestecati cu boia afumata, chimion, ulei si lamaie. Frecati pe pui. Marinati cel putin 2 ore. Gatiti pe gratar mediu 30-40 min intorcand si ungand. Serviti cu salata.', ru: 'Растолките чеснок с солью. Смешайте с копчёной паприкой, кумином, маслом и лимоном. Натрите курицу. Маринуйте минимум 2 часа. Готовьте на среднем гриле 30-40 мин переворачивая и смазывая. Подавайте с салатом.', es: 'Machaque ajo con sal. Mezcle con pimenton ahumado, comino, aceite y limon. Frote sobre pollo. Marine 2 horas. Cocine en parrilla media 30-40 min volteando y barnizando. Sirva con ensalada.' },
